  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to track surgical outcomes and post-operative course in patients
      55 years of age or older treated for ankle fractures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study seeks to describe and track surgical outcomes associated with the use of a
      minimally invasive surgical technique used to treat ankle fractures in at-risk patients 55
      years of age or older
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
